text: Poyma may refer to: *Poyma (river), a river in Primorsky Krai, Russia *Poyma (Biryusa), left tributary of the Biryusa in Irkutsk Oblast, Russia *Poyma, Russia, several rural localities in Russia *Poyma, West Kazakhstan, a village in Terekti District, West Kazakhstan Region, Kazakhstan
title: Poyma
